## Local test (Node script)

This endpoint expects an **Okta access token** (issuer `purpleid.okta.com`), not the FedEx Linehaul **Apigee** JWT used for `linehaul/trip` APIs.

From repo root:

```
OKTA_ACCESS_TOKEN="<paste token from DevTools Network → userinfo request>" node scripts/test-okta-userinfo.mjs
```

Append a successful JSON snapshot to this file:

```
OKTA_ACCESS_TOKEN="..." node scripts/test-okta-userinfo.mjs --append
```

Optional: `node scripts/test-okta-userinfo.mjs <token>` (first arg = token).